File Tagging idea

Search by name/files have been a traditional long lost problem
What if each file was indexed

Non-sensitive files be put through a generic model,
sensitie files be put through a local model on the client.

Creates a logical catalog of files to search and access.

LLM based intepretion of the file and tag generation.
Search tool to sieve through this tag generation or, text match via generated description of the file.
